  "texts": [
    "We run experiments on the Erdős test set (Guo et al. 2025), encompassing 49 topological tasks over 100 graphs each, totaling 4,900 samplesfoot_1.",
    "Across all ablations, shufflings, and models, this amounts to analyzing over 1.5M individual model inferences.",
    "As in Erdős, we group tasks by difficulty (Easy, Medium, Hard, Challenging).",
    "We also introduce a new benchmark of 12 spectral tasks on 100 graphs from the Erdős test set (see App.",
    "Spectral Tasks).Sensitivity to node labeling."
  ],
